
Tips:

1, -m32 / -m64
在64位环境使用-m32/-m64选项指定编译32位程序还是64位程序
gerryyang@TENCENT64;~$gcc -o 32bit_test -m32 32bit_test.c
gerryyang@TENCENT64;~$./32bit_test                       
sizeof(int) 4
sizeof(long) 4
sizeof(p) 4
gerryyang@TENCENT64;~$gcc -o 32bit_test -m64 32bit_test.c
gerryyang@TENCENT64;~$./32bit_test                       
sizeof(int) 4
sizeof(long) 8
sizeof(p) 8




